name: laura felt flower bouquet
description:
Our signature bridal posie bouquet is made with 100% wool felt in beautiful jewel tones of deep purple, teal, brilliant blue, and emerald green with vintage buttons and millinery stamens in the center of each flower. The sturdy handle is wrapped with white and teal silk ribbon and measures 9'' long. 

Go to http://princesslasertron.com/bridal-inquiry for more information about ordering a custom bouquet for your big day. 

Princess Lasertron designed and created the first famous felt flower bouquets which took the wedding market by storm in 2008. As seen in BRIDES magazine, Cosmo Bride, Country Living, Where Women Create, and other national and regional publications as well as countless blogs. For custom orders, please fill out a bridal inquiry form at http://princesslasertron.com/bridal-inquiry
